Name: Blind Bolt A4 Stainless Steel
Description:
Blind Bolts are revolutionary fastening devices used in steel applications where there is no backside access.

The Blind Bolt provides an innovative solution without the need for welding, or expensive tools.

Components can be successfully attached by simply inserting the Blind Bolt, and tightening the nut.
Attribute 2 value(s): 3/8" x 2-3/8",  M8 x 50 (Fits 11/32" Hole),  M10 x 60 (Fits 7/17" Hole),  M12 x 90 (Fits 1/2" Hole),  M16 x 100 (Fits 11/16" Hole)
